GSD.description:
ipvs: fix WARNING in ip_vs_app_net_cleanup()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.8 by commit 97f872b00937f2689bff2dab4ad9ed259482840f, it was introduced in version v2.6.24 by commit 457c4cbc5a3dde259d2a1f15d5f9785290397267. For more details please see the references link.
